  "source": "// Example illustrating control flow with a loop and branches.\n// Loops from `a` up to `b` and\n// uses different builtins depending on the condition.\nseiyaku Example {\n    kotoage fn control(a, b) {\n        for let i = a; i < b; ++i {\n            if i == b {\n                let c = poseidon2(i, b);\n            } else {\n                let c = valcom(i, b);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n",
